- [x] L033 — Now-Casting.com / Cleveland Fed inflation nowcast → `loops/L033-cleveland-fed-inflation-nowcast.md` (Grade B for Cleveland replicate; Grade C for Now-Casting.com paywalled)
- [x] L034 — Dynare + IRIS Toolbox: DSGE open source → `loops/L034-dynare-iris-dsge-landscape.md` (Grade D Block I, C Block II; econpizza + Dynare.jl as the paths)
