### Open data sources + ingestion (L046–L060)
- [x] L046 — World Bank Indicators API: coverage, vintage, rate limits → `loops/L046-world-bank-indicators-api.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW; fourth multi-country adapter after WB/IMF/OECD/BIS)
- [x] L047 — IMF SDMX / IMF Data: granular endpoints → `loops/L047-imf-sdmx-data.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW IFS/WEO/DOT/CPI/COFER; SDMX 3.0 migration is a trap)
- [x] L048 — OECD Data API + ORDRA: how OPENGEM uses it today → `loops/L048-oecd-data-api-beyond-ordra.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW EO+QNA+MEI+CLI alongside ORDRA)
- [x] L049 — BIS Statistics warehouse: full surface → `loops/L049-bis-statistics-warehouse.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW LBS/CBS/EER/CREDIT_GAPS via bulk ZIPs)
- [x] L050 — ECB SDW: euro-area coverage → `loops/L050-ecb-sdw-data-portal.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW; `updatedAfter` + `includeHistory` enable lean refresh + vintage)
- [x] L051 — UN Comtrade + BACI: trade flows → `loops/L051-un-comtrade-baci.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW BACI for annual baseline + ADOPT-BLOCK-II Comtrade for monthly nowcast)
- [x] L052 — IMF DOTS: trade flows → `loops/L052-imf-dots-vs-un-comtrade.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW DOTS/IMTS as headline bilateral panel; rides existing IMF adapter)
- [x] L053 — IEA / EIA / Our World in Data energy → `loops/L053-energy-iea-eia-owid.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW EIA+OWID; IEA paywalled + NC license blocks ingestion)
- [x] L054 — Climate / weather TSI (NOAA, ECMWF ERA5) for macro link → `loops/L054-climate-weather-as-macro-signal.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW GHCN/CDO; ADOPT-BLOCK-II ERA5 via CDS)
- [x] L055 — Shipping: PortWatch, MarineTraffic AIS, IMF PortWatch API → `loops/L055-shipping-portwatch-ais-opensky.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW PortWatch; MarineTraffic enterprise-only)
- [x] L056 — Commodity prices: World Bank Pink Sheet, IMF Primary → `loops/L056-commodity-prices.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW both; CRB/BCOM proprietary)
- [x] L057 — Currency / FX free-tier APIs (ECB, exchangerate.host, FRB H.10) → `loops/L057-fx-free-apis.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW ECB Eurofxref + BIS EER + FRB H.10; resellers are funnel-ware)
- [x] L058 — Equity indices free APIs (Stooq, Yahoo Finance via yfinance, Alpaca) → `loops/L058-equities-free-apis.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW Stooq; yfinance is fragile)
- [x] L059 — Treasury yield curves / DRD daily series → `loops/L059-treasury-yields-sovereign-bonds.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW DTYC+DTRYC + G7 direct central-bank feeds)
- [x] L060 — Crypto on-chain macro proxies (Glassnode, CoinMetrics community tier) → `loops/L060-crypto-onchain-macro-proxies.md` (Verdict: ADOPT-NOW CoinMetrics+DeFiLlama+Blockchain.com; CC-BY-NC tag enforcement required)

